the zero &lt;unk&gt; is a 2014 science fiction science fiction film directed by terry gilliam , written by gilliam and nicolas &lt;unk&gt; , based on the novel of the same name by lajos bíró . the film was selected to be screened in the contemporary world cinema section at the 2014 toronto international film festival . the film was selected as the swiss entry for the best foreign language film at the 87th academy awards , but was not accepted as a nominee .